Package FoodModels

Class Food

java.lang.Object
FoodModels.Food
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFromJSON, IToJSON, Comparable
public class Food extends Object implements IToJSON, Comparable, IFromJSON
This class represents a food item with its nutritional information and properties.
